  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1102</quote_ID>
    <quoter>朱熹</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1102</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>程子曰 習 重習也 時復思繹 浹洽於中 則說也 又曰 學者 將以行之也 時習之 則所學者在我 故 悅 </quote_text>
    <wording>程子曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1105</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1103</quote_ID>
    <quoter>朱熹</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1102</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>謝氏曰 時習者 無時而不習 坐如尸 坐時習也 立如齊 立時習也</quote_text>
    <wording>謝氏曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1106</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1104</quote_ID>
    <quoter>朱熹</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1102</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>程子曰 以善及人 而信從者衆 故 可樂 又曰 說 在心 樂 主發散 在外</quote_text>
    <wording>程子曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1105</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1105</quote_ID>
    <quoter>朱熹</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1102</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>尹氏曰 學 在己 知不知 在人 何慍之有 </quote_text>
    <wording>尹氏曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1107</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1106</quote_ID>
    <quoter>朱熹</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1102</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>程子曰 雖樂於及人 不見是而無悶 乃所謂君子 </quote_text>
    <wording>程子曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1105</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1107</quote_ID>
    <quoter>朱熹</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1102</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>程子曰 樂 由說而後得 非樂 不足以語君子</quote_text>
    <wording>程子曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1105</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1108</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>邢曰稱師曰子_公羊傳曰子沈子 何休云稱子冠氏上者 著其爲師也_直言子曰者 以其聖德著聞 師範來世 不須言其氏 人盡知之也</quote_text>
    <wording>邢曰_公羊傳曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1104</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1109</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>_荻云孔門稱夫子曰子者 內辭也 如春秋稱魯君曰公_</quote_text>
    <wording>荻云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1103</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1110</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>皇云懷抱欣暢也 </quote_text>
    <wording>皇云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1108</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1111</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>兌卦上開。夬卦亦然。悅快義相近也。兌卦彖傳云說以先民</quote_text>
    <wording>兌卦</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1112</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>樂。深喜也_朱子曰悅是感於外而發於中。樂是充於中而溢於外_ </quote_text>
    <wording>朱子曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1101</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1113</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>人不知。謂人不知我之學成也。慍。心有所蘊結也_詩檜風云我心蘊結兮_ </quote_text>
    <wording>詩</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1114</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>易曰不見是而无悶_程子云_</quote_text>
    <wording>程子云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1105</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1115</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>鄭玄玉藻注曰君子。大夫士_又云君子士已上_ </quote_text>
    <wording>鄭玄玉藻注曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1109</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1116</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>少儀注曰君子。卿大夫_孟子云非野人。莫養君子_</quote_text>
    <wording>少儀注曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1117</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>_賈誼新書引逸禮。小學業小道。大學業大道_</quote_text>
    <wording>賈誼新書</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1110</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1118</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>駁曰非也。學記曰人不學。不知道。孔子曰吾十有五志于學。此方是業道之名。</quote_text>
    <wording>學記曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1119</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>說文曰學覺也。謂先覺覺後覺也。然此亦造字之原義。非此經之所宜引</quote_text>
    <wording>說文曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1120</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>侃曰學有三時 一身中時_學記云時過然後學則勤苦而難成_</quote_text>
    <wording>侃曰_學記云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1108</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1121</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>二年中時_王制云春秋敎以禮樂 冬夏敎以詩書_ </quote_text>
    <wording>王制云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1122</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>三日中時_學記云藏焉脩焉息焉游焉 是日日所習也_</quote_text>
    <wording>學記云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1123</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>駁曰非也。時習者。時時習之也_朱子云_</quote_text>
    <wording>朱子云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1101</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1124</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>學晨省昏定。便自是日習晨省昏定。學日乾夕惕。便自是日習日乾夕惕。學祭禮習祭禮。學鄕禮習鄕禮_飮射投壺等_ 學樂習樂_月令云孟春命樂正入學習舞。季秋命樂正人學習吹_ 學誦習誦。學射御習射御_月令云孟冬習射御_ 學書數習書數。皆所以肄業也。</quote_text>
    <wording>月令云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1125</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>王曰學者。以時誦習之</quote_text>
    <wording>王曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1111</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1126</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>駁曰非也。誦習而已者。後世之學也。禮樂射御。可習者多。奚但誦而已。易曰朋友講習_兌大象_講者論辨也。無所不包。誦則詩書而已。學止是哉。</quote_text>
    <wording>易曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1127</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>引證 大戴禮曰君子旣學之。患其不博也。旣博之。患其不習也_曾子立事篇_</quote_text>
    <wording>大戴禮曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1128</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>包曰同門曰朋 駁曰非也 </quote_text>
    <wording>包曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID>PESN_1112</person_ID>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1129</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>公羊傳云同門曰朋_兌卦疏_</quote_text>
    <wording>公羊傳云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1130</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>周禮注云同師曰朋_大司徒聯朋友之注_ </quote_text>
    <wording>周禮注云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1131</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>集注云同類曰朋。總之朋者。志同而意合者也。何必同門</quote_text>
    <wording>集注云</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1132</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>何曰凡人有所不知。君子不怒_邢云古之學者爲己。含章內映。他人不知。而我不怒也。一云若有人鈍根不能知解者。君子恕之而不怒也_</quote_text>
    <wording>何曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1133</quote_ID>
    <quoter>丁若鏞</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1105</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>或曰夫子一生。學不厭敎不倦。此正指誨人一節。故魏文靖講學余山。有學者辨論不釋。怫形于色。文靖曰人不自知。于我何慍。正得此意</quote_text>
    <wording>文靖曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1134</quote_ID>
    <quoter>荻生徂徠</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1106</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>子為男子美稱 亦為大夫之稱 古者天子世嗣 諸侯世嗣 大夫不世爵 士不世官 </quote_text>
    <wording>古者</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID> </Book_ID>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1135</quote_ID>
    <quoter>荻生徂徠</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1106</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>四十而仕為士 五十而爵為大夫 七十致仕 是德立而爵從 以大夫為其至 者 非若秦漢以後士 生願封侯 以官至三公為分所當得者比也 是稱子之義也</quote_text>
    <wording> 《禮記》</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1136</quote_ID>
    <quoter>荻生徂徠</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1106</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>論語稱孔子去姓 如春秋公魯侯 内辭也 </quote_text>
    <wording>春秋</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1137</quote_ID>
    <quoter>荻生徂徠</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1106</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>傳曰樂正崇四術 立四教 順先王詩書禮樂以造士 是也 </quote_text>
    <wording>傳曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1138</quote_ID>
    <quoter>荻生徂徠</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1106</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>習者 肄其業也 時習之 王肅曰 以時誦習之 </quote_text>
    <wording>王肅曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1139</quote_ID>
    <quoter>荻生徂徠</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1106</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>𫝊曰 春誦夏絃秋學禮冬讀書 其習之亦如之 以身處先王之教也 </quote_text>
    <wording>𫝊曰</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
  <item>
    <quote_ID>QUOT_1140</quote_ID>
    <quoter>荻生徂徠</quoter>
    <comment_ID>COMT_1106</comment_ID>
    <quote_text>凡天下之樂 皆在富貴 而貧賤之樂 其大而可皆能者 唯是已 故自西自東 自南自北 無思不服 文王之詩 而孔子迺足當之矣</quote_text>
    <wording>故</wording>
    <origin_text/>
    <person_ID/>
    <Book_ID/>
    <purpose_point/>
  </item>
